## Limitations

This report is limited by the availability of recent data and studies specifically focused on athletes. The perception of increased incidents may be influenced by media coverage rather than actual statistical increases. Additionally, the complexity of diagnosing genetic heart conditions means that some cases may remain unexplained. Further research is needed to explore preventive measures and improve early detection of at-risk individuals.

